title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 12 2022

description:
Democrat chattering class talks up Hillary in 2024. Clay theory: Will Dems make midterms a referendum on abortion? McConnell calls out Biden's segregationist BS. Djokovic, Rodgers, Irving: Sports stars stand up for covid freedom. Buck never asks for autographs, but says he just might for his Rodgers jersey "that I still need to order."
